data.title: Graduate Research Forum
data.text:
The Graduate Research Forum, a part of the Student Research Week Student Research Week researchweek.ucf.edu, features poster displays and oral presentations representing UCF graduate students from diverse disciplines. The Graduate Research Forum is an opportunity for graduate students to showcase their research and creative projects and to receive valuable feedback from faculty judges. Awards for presentations deemed exemplary are given.

UCF is canceling Student Research Week 2020, including the Graduate Research Forum. We thank you for your hard work and dedication to research and regret that this outbreak has necessitated this action. However, your safety is our top priority, which is why we have made this decision.

For more details visit: Graduate Research Forum

Questions? Please email researchweek@ucf.edu.
